'''亚当·哈特-戴维斯'''（{{lang-en|Adam Hart-Davis}}，{{bd|1943年|7月4日|}}）是一位[[英国|英国]]科學家、作家、攝影師、歷史學家和廣播員，参加过[[BBC|BBC]]制作的《[[明日的世界_(電視節目)|明日的世界]]》（''Tomorrow's World''）等电视节目<ref>{{cite news|last=Knapton|first=Sarah|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/science/2017/05/02/tomorrows-world-returns-bbc-startling-warning-stephen-hawking/|title=Tomorrow’s World returns to BBC with startling warning from Stephen Hawking – we must leave Earth|date=5 May 2017|work=The Daily Telegraph|accessdate=2 May 2017|language=en-GB|issn=0307-1235|archive-date=2017-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170505013510/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/science/2017/05/02/tomorrows-world-returns-bbc-startling-warning-stephen-hawking/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，写作过《时间是什么》（''The Book of Time''，2010）<ref>{{cite book |title=Shi jian shi shen me = The book of time |publisher=Hu nan ke xue ji shu chu ban she |location=Zhangsha |isbn=9787535792990 |edition=Di 1 ban}}</ref>等科普书籍。

